      "content": "okay i get it, but honestly everything else i've tried isn't working. what about an antibiotic then? my sinus pain is really throbbing and feels like it's turning into a fever. i have some ciprofloxacin in the cabinet from a different infection a few months ago. would taking a couple of those be safer for the baby since it's for the infection itself? i just really need to know if i can take something tonight.",
